@node "Introduction" "Introduction"
@next "Distribution"
@prev "Main"
@{b}Introduction@{ub}

CatalogueStats is a small statistics generator for the
filecatalogue.  I have had it running in my BBS for making a
bulletin for well over one year.  I thought I'd release it for
others to enjoy it.

@endnode

@node "Distribution" "Distribution"
@next "Responsibility"
@prev "Introduction"
@{b}Distribution@{ub}

This version of CatalogueStats is freely distributable for
non-commercial use.

You can spread this complete archive via AmiNet, ADS, SAN and
otherĀnon-profit networks and BBS:es.

@endnode

